<!-- SECTION 1 -->
<div class="card">
<h3>1Ô∏è‚É£ Go to Texas DPS Yourself</h3>

<p>Even if they told you it would be mailed, you can apply directly.</p>

<p><strong>Bring:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Release paperwork</li>
<li>Prison ID (even if expired)</li>
<li>Social Security card (if available)</li>
<li>Birth certificate (if available)</li>
</ul>

<p>Find DPS locations:</p>
<p><a href="https://www.dps.texas.gov/section/driver-license/driver-license-office-locations" target="_blank">
Texas DPS Office Locator
</a></p>

<p><strong>Ask for a temporary paper ID while you wait.</strong></p>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 2 -->
<div class="card">
<h3>2Ô∏è‚É£ If You Do Not Have a Social Security Card</h3>

<p>Go to a Social Security office and request a replacement card (free).</p>

<p><strong>Bring:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Release paperwork</li>
<li>Any identification you have</li>
<li>Birth certificate (if possible)</li>
</ul>

<p>Find office:</p>
<p><a href="https://www.ssa.gov/locator/" target="_blank">
Social Security Office Locator
</a></p>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 3 -->
<div class="card">
<h3>3Ô∏è‚É£ If You Do Not Have a Birth Certificate</h3>

<p>Order it from Texas Vital Records:</p>

<p><a href="https://www.dshs.texas.gov/vs" target="_blank">
Texas Vital Statistics
</a></p>

<p>Or contact the county where you were born.</p>

<p>Many nonprofits will help pay the fee.</p>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 4 -->
<div class="card">
<h3>4Ô∏è‚É£ You CAN Start Job Searching Without ID</h3>

<p>You cannot complete hiring paperwork without proper ID,  
but you CAN:</p>

<ul>
<li>Apply for jobs</li>
<li>Attend interviews</li>
<li>Explain your ID is being processed</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>What to say:</strong></p>

<div class="success">
‚ÄúMy state ID is currently being processed. I have applied and expect it within a few weeks. I can provide documentation showing it is in progress.‚Äù
</div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 5 -->
<div class="card">
<h3>5Ô∏è‚É£ If Prison Never Submitted It</h3>

<p>Call your unit‚Äôs:</p>
<ul>
<li>Reentry office</li>
<li>Records department</li>
<li>Classification officer</li>
</ul>

<p>Ask:</p>
<ul>
<li>Was my ID application submitted?</li>
<li>When?</li>
<li>What address was used?</li>
</ul>

<p>Sometimes it was mailed to the wrong address.</p>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 6 -->
